<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有客人来玩<delay8 />
就会很热闹，真棒呢！<delay frames="40" />
请一定要多坐一会儿。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我的房间
并没有多了不起，<delay20 />
但还是请你<delay8 />多坐坐。<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />如果因为太无聊而感到困倦了，<delay8 />
那就对不起了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对不起，<delay20 />难得你来玩，
我却感觉迷迷糊糊的<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我这种状态<delay8 />就是所谓的
“半梦半醒”吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的目标是打造一间
能让人放松的房间。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算因为太放松<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而不小心打起瞌睡来
也没关系哦！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才我读了一本书，<delay20 />
名字叫做
《梦之国的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />》！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然是在梦境里读的，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但非常有趣。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我做梦都没想到
今天<delay8 />会有客人来玩，<delay20 />
所以能见到你真是令人高兴！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然房间有点乱，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但还请你多能坐一会儿！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>